{"tha-ap221:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap221:0.2":"Hatthivagga ","tha-ap221:0.3":"Sappidayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap221:1.1":"“Nisinno pasadavare, ","tha-ap221:1.2":"nariganapurakkhato; ","tha-ap221:1.3":"Byadhitam samanam disva, ","tha-ap221:1.4":"abhinamesaham gharam. ","tha-ap221:2.1":"Upavittham mahaviram, ","tha-ap221:2.2":"devadevam narasabham; ","tha-ap221:2.3":"Sappitelam maya dinnam, ","tha-ap221:2.4":"siddhatthassa mahesino. ","tha-ap221:3.1":"Passaddhadaratham disva, ","tha-ap221:3.2":"vippasannamukhindriyam; ","tha-ap221:3.3":"Vanditva satthuno pade, ","tha-ap221:3.4":"anusamsavayim pure. ","tha-ap221:4.1":"Disva mam suppasannattam, ","tha-ap221:4.2":"iddhiya paramingato; ","tha-ap221:4.3":"Nabham abbhuggami dhiro, ","tha-ap221:4.4":"hamsarajava ambare. ","tha-ap221:5.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap221:5.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","tha-ap221:5.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap221:5.4":"sappitelassidam phalam. ","tha-ap221:6.1":"Ito sattarase kappe, ","tha-ap221:6.2":"jutideva sanamako; ","tha-ap221:6.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap221:6.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap221:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap221:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap221:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap221:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sappidayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap221:9.1":"Sappidayakattherassapadanam navamam. "}